Songs of Praise - Gospel Choir of the Year (2/2)


BBC One, 4:15PM Sun, 13 Oct 2013

Judges Ruby Turner, Bazil Meade and Carrie Grant face the difficult task of selecting the best gospel choir from six remarkable finalists for this Songs of Praise competition from Birmingham Town Hall, introduced by David Grant.
